-Swedish éclairs.
-Oh!

1:09:01.683 --> 1:09:02.893
They're a little messy.

1:09:03.769 --> 1:09:05.187
-But let's try.
-Yes.

1:09:05.270 --> 1:09:06.313
With your finger.

1:09:10.734 --> 1:09:12.361
Mmm!

1:09:14.613 --> 1:09:16.323
How did you find this place?

1:09:17.198 --> 1:09:18.658
This was Sonya's place.

1:09:21.036 --> 1:09:23.580
We used to come here
every Saturday at- 00.

1:09:25.874 --> 1:09:27.417
And then? What?

1:09:28.001 --> 1:09:29.252
Go home at- 00.

1:09:30.546 --> 1:09:32.548
I'd wash and wax the car,

1:09:32.631 --> 1:09:37.176
and she would grade her papers and cook
and spend the rest of the day reading.

1:09:37.803 --> 1:09:39.095
What kind of books?

1:09:40.346 --> 1:09:41.974
-Her books.

1:09:43.267 --> 1:09:45.519
I tried to read some of them, but...

1:09:45.602 --> 1:09:46.603
I'm just...

1:09:47.395 --> 1:09:48.522
I'm not into books.

1:09:49.982 --> 1:09:52.109
