what they were doing until we told them,

1:11:41.760 --> 1:11:42.761
Reuben and I.

1:11:43.470 --> 1:11:45.013
But this was before the coup?

1:11:45.097 --> 1:11:47.850
Oh, yeah, yeah.
Reuben and I were friends then.

1:11:47.933 --> 1:11:51.478
After that,
all we saw were the differences.

1:12:22.301 --> 1:12:26.722
A few years later, their son, Chris,
he, uh, took a job in Japan,

1:12:26.805 --> 1:12:29.349
and I don't think
he's been back to visit them since.

1:12:30.517 --> 1:12:32.519
-Oh.
-Reuben and he never did get along.

1:12:33.520 --> 1:12:36.190
Anyway, that's when I decided
to bury the hatchet.

1:12:36.273 --> 1:12:37.274
Reuben.

1:12:39.109 --> 1:12:40.319
Hey.

1:12:41.653 --> 1:12:44.156
Sonya gave me this a while back.

1:12:44.239 --> 1:12:45.866
Never found the occasion.

1:12:47.284 --> 1:12:49.870
I thought maybe we could start fresh.

1:12:53.999 --> 1:12:56.210
Hey, would you like to see my new car?

1:12:57.836 --> 1:12:58.962
Sure.

1:12:59.046 --> 1:13:00.214
It's a new model.

1:13:00.881 --> 1:13:02.341
Just came out.

1:13:07.971 --> 1:13:09.014
Voilà.

1:13:11.558 --> 1:13:12.476
A Toyota?

1:13:14.102 --> 1:13:15.979
You bought a Toyota.

1:13:16.063 --> 1:13:18.023
Celica GT convertible.

1:13:18.106 --> 1:13:20.526
Five-speed automatic.

1:13:21.193 --> 1:13:23.153
You gotta change with the times.

1:13:24.071 --> 1:13:25.197
Otto!

1:13:27.032 --> 1:13:31.036
I don't know what went wrong with Reuben,
but that's when I knew I'd lost him.

1:13:31.119 --> 1:13:33.288
I mean, a man has to stand up
for what he believes in.

1:13:33.372 --> 1:13:36.041
Even if it is an F-O-R-D.

1:13:39.253 --> 1:13:43.632
And you and Sonya,
did you ever think about having children?

1:13:47.678 --> 1:13:49.596
Well,- 00.

1:13:51.974 --> 1:13:52.975
Okay.

1:13:54.810 --> 1:13:55.811
Yes.

1:14:01.024 --> 1:14:03.819
I was wondering
if you could help us out tonight.

1:14:03.902 --> 1:14:06.613
Me and Tommy don't get a lot of time
to go out for dinner

1:14:06.697 --> 1:14:07.990
before the baby comes.

1:14:08.073 --> 1:14:10.409
I'm not gonna drive you two
around on a date.

1:14:10.993 --> 1:14:13.871
No. We're gonna take a cab.

1:14:14.955 --> 1:14:16.707
What do you need me for, then?

1:14:16.790 --> 1:14:19.960
-Mama, I did not! Why would I?
-Yes, you did!

1:14:20.043 --> 1:14:21.795
-Give it back!
-You gotta catch me!

1:14:21.879 --> 1:14:23.714
You guys, por favor.

1:14:28.468 --> 1:14:30.762
And learn to share your everything.

1:14:32.097 --> 1:14:33.640
I'm not sure about this.

1:14:33.724 --> 1:14:36.727
No. Don't be silly.
It's gonna be very fun.

1:14:36.810 --> 1:14:40.606
If you remember,
Abbie has to be in bed by- 00, okay?

1:14:40.689 --> 1:14:42.024
-You're good?

1:14:43.525 --> 1:14:46.862
So, alarm code, 4491. 4491.

1:14:46.945 --> 1:14:50.115
I'm setting it to "Armed Stay."
Are you paying attention?

1:14:50.199 --> 1:14:51.825
So if you wanna go out,

1:14:51.909 --> 1:14:55.162
you just have to press this button here,
and it's disalarmed.

1:14:55.245 --> 1:14:56.997
I'll be right here.

1:14:58.081 --> 1:14:59.333
Right. Yeah.

1:15:00.292 --> 1:15:01.668
Well, you never know.

1:15:01.752 --> 1:15:03.504
Be good to Abuelo Otto please, okay?

1:15:03.587 --> 1:15:04.713
We will!

1:15:08.926 --> 1:15:10.636
I don't see chocolate milk in here.

1:15:10.719 --> 1:15:14.473
You make it with the syrup.
But not too much. It'll keep her awake.

1:15:16.642 --> 1:15:17.935
Give me milk.

1:15:18.018 --> 1:15:19.269
What is that?

1:15:19.353 --> 1:15:22.231
That's the goddamn useless dishwasher.

1:15:23.941 --> 1:15:26.485
Dad said he wanted
to throw it out the window,

1:15:26.568 --> 1:15:28.987
but Mom said Dad isn't allowed
to open windows anymore.

1:15:34.785 --> 1:15:35.786
Head.

1:15:36.870 --> 1:15:37.871
Cabeza.

1:15:38.664 --> 1:15:40.499
-Cabeza.

1:15:40.582 --> 1:15:41.458
Good.

1:15:42.334 --> 1:15:43.210
Eyes.

1:15:43.794 --> 1:15:44.795
Ojos.

1:15:44.878 --> 1:15:47.381
-Ojos.

1:15:49.049 --> 1:15:49.883
Good.

1:15:49.967 --> 1:15:52.010
Arm. Brazo.

1:15:52.094 --> 1:15:54.346
Arm. Brazo.

1:15:54.429 --> 1:15:55.305
Good.

