I don't think this is a good idea.

1:16:03.313 --> 1:16:04.523
Why?

1:16:05.649 --> 1:16:08.485
Because no one stands a chance
against a luchadoro.

1:16:08.569 --> 1:16:10.988
Abuelo Luchadoro!

