Talk to me, Otto.

1:24:01.750 --> 1:24:02.751
Otto.

1:24:06.255 --> 1:24:07.589
Otto.

1:24:25.566 --> 1:24:26.733
Thank you.

1:24:56.555 --> 1:24:58.265
It'll be cute on you.

1:24:58.348 --> 1:24:59.933
-No.
-Aw, c'mon.

1:25:00.017 --> 1:25:03.145
Honey, you look really cute.

1:27:47.726 --> 1:27:49.144
Give me your hand.

1:27:49.228 --> 1:27:50.812
The baby's really kicking.

1:28:03.867 --> 1:28:05.077
I'll be right back.

