♪ I should be hoping
But I can't stop thinking ♪

1:30:21.547 --> 1:30:22.548
Hi.

1:30:23.215 --> 1:30:26.134
♪ Oh ♪

1:30:26.218 --> 1:30:27.135
There you are.

1:30:27.219 --> 1:30:29.596
♪ Of all the things we should've said
That we never said ♪

